posting_body: ['Morrowood Townhomes', 'Leasing Office:', '5915 Trammell Rd', 'Morrow, GA 30260', 'show contact info', 'Take a look at what Morrowood Townhomes has to offer!', 'Morrow houses part of the Reynolds Nature Preserve and Big Pond.', 'Take advantage of the wildlife viewing opportunities on the rolling hills, forests, and wetlands.', 'Morrow also surrounds the north end of Lake Louise!', 'Rental Information:', '3 Bedroom / 2.5 Bathroom / 1521 sq ft / $1620 - $4049/Month', 'Lease Terms:', '6-Month, 12-Month', 'Apartment Amenities:', '◾ Ceiling Fans', '◾ Dining Room', '◾ Dishwasher', '◾ Frost-Free Refrigerator', '◾ Kitchen', '◾ Range', '◾ Refrigerator', '◾', 'Tub/Shower', '◾ Wall to Wall Carpeting', '◾ Cable TV/High Speed Internet Ready', '◾ Central Air Conditioning and Heating', '◾ Private Patio or Balcony', '◾ Spacious Floor Plans', '◾ Vaulted Ceilings in Select Units', '◾ Vinyl Flooring', '◾ Walk-In & Double Closets', '◾ Washer/Dryer Hookup', '◾ Window Coverings', 'Additional Information:', '◾ 24-Hour Emergency Maintenance Service', '◾ BBQ/Picnic Area', '◾ Laundry Facilities', '◾ On-Site Maintenance/Management', '◾ Pet Play Area', '◾ Sparkling Swimming Pool', '◾', 'Well Equipped One-Acre Playground', '◾ Wi-Fi at Pool and Clubhouse', '◾ Convenient Online Rental Payments', '◾ Convenient to Southlake Mall, Clayton State University & Hospitals', '◾ Easy Access to International Airport, Highways, & Interstates 75, 285 & 675', '◾ Free Pest Control', '◾ Lush, Professionally Maintained Landscaping', '◾ Package Service', '◾ Pet Friendly', '◾ Resident Referral Program', 'Leasing Hours:', 'Mon - Fri: 9:00 AM - 6:00 PM', 'Sat: 10:00 AM - 4:00 PM', 'show contact info', 'Pet Policy:', 'Pets Welcome!', 'Non-aggressive breeds accepted.', 'Weight Restrictions may apply.', 'Please see the office for fees & other details!', 'Management Company:', 'Peak Living', 'EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY', '2EF24287567441']
